Description_lang: Your Wrath and Starfire chance to critically strike is increased by $s1% and they generate ${$s2/10} additional Astral Power.

description_blz.en_US: Your Wrath and Starfire chance to critically strike is increased by 10% and they generate 2 additional Astral Power.
description_blz.es_MX: La probabilidad de que tu Cólera y Fuego estelar asesten un golpe crítico aumenta un 10% y generan 2 p. más de poder astral.
description_blz.pt_BR: A chance da sua Ira e do seu Fogo Estelar acertarem criticamente aumenta em 10% e ambos geram mais 2 de Poder Astral.
description_blz.de_DE: Eure Fähigkeiten 'Zorn' und 'Sternenfeuer' haben eine um 10% erhöhte kritische Trefferchance und erzeugen zusätzlich 2 Astrale Macht.
description_blz.en_GB: Your Wrath and Starfire chance to critically strike is increased by 10% and they generate 2 additional Astral Power.
description_blz.es_ES: Aumenta 10% tus probabilidades de asestar un golpe crítico con Cólera y Fuego estelar. Además, genera 2 p. de poder astral extra.
description_blz.fr_FR: Les chances de coup critique de Colère et Feu stellaire sont augmentées 10% et ces sorts génèrent 2 points de puissance astrale supplémentaires.
description_blz.it_IT: Aumenta la probabilità di critico di Ira Silvana e Fuoco Stellare del 10% e aumenta di 2 il potere astrale che generano.
description_blz.ru_RU: Вероятность критического удара "Гнева" и "Звездного огня" увеличена на 10%. Кроме того, они дают на 2 больше астральной мощи.
description_blz.ko_KR: 천벌과 별빛섬광의 치명타 및 극대화율이 10%만큼 증가하고 2의 천공의 힘을 추가로 생성합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 你的憤怒和星火術的致命一擊機率提高10%，並額外產生2點星能。
description_blz.zh_CN: 你的愤怒和星火术的爆击几率提高10%，并额外产生2点星界能量。
